data.title: List of Nobel Prize Laureates (1901-2011)
data.meta_description: List of Nobel Prize Laureates (1901-2011) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document lists all Nobel laureates from 1901 to 1960. It provides the names of individuals and organizations that were awarded Nobel Prizes each year in the categories of Physics, Chemistry, Physiology or Medicine, Literature, Peace, and Economics (established in 1968). Some key details are also given about the history and administration of the Nobel Prizes.
